          "description": "Dr.Tun is patient, thorough, and kind. He took the time to listen to my concerns (I brought a list) and address EVERY. SINGLE. ONE. He listened to me. I was not rushed out. I've seen some reviews upset about a long wait time. You are waiting because he pays attention to all of his patients and heps them through understanding what they are dealing with. I would wait 10 hours to see him. He's THAT good. He managed to put my anxious mind at ease, and I am so grateful that I found him. I recommend him to anyone who is looking for a primary care physician. The man is on point.",
